<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Citadel </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1993, Citadel Real estate can be rightly touted as one of the most desirable and well-designed neighborhoods in NW Calgary. With elaborate walking trails and bike pathways maneuvering around the community and providing easy access to the plethora of play structures, baseball diamonds, soccer fields, skating rinks, tennis courts, Citadel offers a variety of recreational activities for the residents to make the most of their leisurely hours.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">A family oriented neighborhood, the community in Citadel attracts home buyers from all walks of life including the young, growing families and retirees alike.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">With the total built-up areas somewhere between 1000 square ft to 2500 square ft Citadel homes for sale predominately comprise of townhouses, single family homes, and condo units.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Though there is no community center here, a community association oversees most of the community-related tasks. The neighborhood has several pathways that lead to the central hub, which is known for its luscious green spaces.</p>
        </div>
